summary: I have been pursuing and nurturing the passion towards Communications since I did not know academic definitions of it. Experienced in doing PR, Marketing and Project management in voluntary organizations equips me skills, knowledge and experiences to keep moving forward, complete myself day by day. And finally, activate the leadership!

projects:
[{'title': 'Digital magazine', 'date': {'start': {'month': 9, 'day': None, 'year': 2021}, 'end': {'month': 11, 'day': None, 'year': 2021}}, 'description': "Journey - a digital magazine that guides students, who are studying in the International School of Business (ISB) at HAN University of Applied Sciences, to explore and achieve balance in their well-being.

The magazine was chosen by our client - the International School of Business, which made our team become the winner in the competition between five teams to create a digital magazine for students at ISB. After intensive six weeks, I learned a lot about how to adapt to multicultural teammates, be fast and decisive when an issue happens such as one of my teammates was low performed because of personal problems, be a good listener to interpret thoroughly what my partner was saying and then I could respond it appropriately.

It's a short period but It leaves lots of lesson learned for me, and help me find out my strengths in creativity, managing and leadership.", 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Que Anh (Annie)', 'last_name': 'Tran Ngoc', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Vice Head of Program Department at VSNL - Vietnamese Student Association in the Netherlands'}, {'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Nina', 'last_name': 'Top', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Communication Studies @ HAN University'}]}]
